OL,3,CPeston: Starmer has handed his future
OL,4,Cto Burnham
OL,6,FI think we can safely assume that the
OL,7,Fnext truly compelling episode in
OL,8,FLabour's real-time soap opera,
OL,9,Fentitled "Get Starmer", will be the by-
OL,10,Felection in Makerfield.
OL,12,FSubject to Labour's ruling NEC
OL,13,Fallowing Andy Burnham to stand there -
OL,14,Fand Downing Street says the prime
OL,15,Fminister has dropped his objections,
OL,16,Fso permission will be given -
OL,17,FBurnham's sotto voce campaign slogan
OL,18,Fwill be unusual.
OL,20,FIt will be "Vote Burnham to sack
OL,21,FStarmer."
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@VO]|D@LOU}D@IO]
