PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778839649
OL,3,CPeston: Starmer has handed his future
OL,4,Cto Burnham
OL,6,FSo Starmer seems to be in the
OL,7,Funcomfortable position of being a
OL,8,Fbystander in the events that will
OL,9,Fshape his own destiny.
OL,11,FAnd as for the country, there are
OL,12,Fweeks more of destabilising
OL,13,Funcertainty about who is really in
OL,14,Fcharge, or who will be running this
OL,15,Fplace just weeks from now.
OL,17,FMakerfield will make history, one way
OL,18,For another.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
